Vendored ION-DTN private headers
================================

bpP.h is an internal Bundle Protocol header that ION-DTN does NOT install to
its include prefix, yet the MQTT CLA sources require it. A verbatim copy is
kept here so this contribution can be built against an *installed* ION without
needing an ION source checkout.

Provenance: ION-DTN 4.1.4, bpv7/library/bpP.h

Keep this copy in sync with the ION-DTN version you have installed. The struct
layouts it declares must match the installed libbp/libici, or the daemons will
misbehave at runtime.
1